## 10. 查询与撤单

### 查询订单 `GET /api/v1/order`

```python
# 查未成交订单
adapter._get('/api/v1/order', query={
    'filter': '{"open": true}'
})

# 查特定订单
adapter._get('/api/v1/order', query={
    'filter': '{"orderID": "xxx-xxx-xxx"}'
})
```

返回关键字段：`orderID`, `ordStatus`, `avgPx`, `cumQty`, `leavesQty`

### 撤单 `DELETE /api/v1/order`

```python
# 撤单个订单
adapter._delete('/api/v1/order', data={'orderID': 'xxx-xxx-xxx'})

# 按客户端 ID 撤
adapter._delete('/api/v1/order', data={'clOrdID': 'my-order-001'})
```

### 撤所有 `DELETE /api/v1/order/all`

```python
# 撤所有
adapter._delete('/api/v1/order/all')

# 只撤某个币种
adapter._delete('/api/v1/order/all', data={'symbol': 'ETHUSDT'})
```

